description: Depression is the number one cause of non-fatal disability in Australia. However, it does not have to be tolerated as a life-long condition. It is reversible. In this program, Gary Kent interviews Neil Nedley, MD, a practicing internal medicine specialist and the author of Depression, the Way Out. Dr. Nedley shares with us the ways to recognize the symptoms of depression and get effective help. For those in the grip of this dark and lonely disease, Dr. Nedley brings hope.
